788
00:38:11,853 --> 00:38:14,039
C'est ça le pire, hein ?

789
00:38:18,180 --> 00:38:19,805
On est ensemble.

790
00:38:19,905 --> 00:38:21,743
On plongera ensemble.

791
00:38:22,833 --> 00:38:23,813
Paige ?

792
00:38:24,132 --> 00:38:25,525
C'est Bennett.

793
00:38:26,725 --> 00:38:28,550
Je pensais pas que
tu m'appellerais.

794
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:29,524
Ouais.

795
